                    <ab>(C.) In nomine sanctae et individuae trinitatis. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/173">Otto</persName> divina favente
                        clementia imperator augustus. Si sanctis ac venerabilibus locis ea quae ab
                        antecessoribus nostris collata sunt, corroborare studuerimus et de his que
                        nostri iuris sunt concedere satagimus, aeterne vite emolumentum adipisci ac
                        presentis status soliditatem propensius augmentari non titubamus. Idcirco
                        omnium fidelium sanctae dei ecclesiae nostrorumque presentium ac futurorum
                        industria noverit, <rs key="#Abbots">abbatem</rs> et <rs key="#Monks"
                            >monachos</rs> in <rs key="#Monasteries">coenobio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Decima #Public_exactions #Angaria #Churches #Monasteries #Cells/hermitages #Abbots #Monks #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/301">domini et salvatoris nostri Iesu
                            Christi</orgName> militantes in <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Decima #Public_exactions #Angaria #Churches #Monasteries #Cells/hermitages #Abbots #Monks #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#places/737">monte Amiate</placeName> nobis lacrimabiliter
                        protulisse, quod famis ac nuditatis indigentia ibidem deo servire non
                        possent, eo quod <rs key="#Curtes">cortes</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Cells/hermitages">celle</rs> que a precessoribus ad sumptum eorum
                        conlate sunt, a pravis fuissent distracte hominibus. Nos quidem pro dei
                        amore animarumque nostrarum remedio, quoniam idem coenobium in nostram
                        devenerat <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">potestatem ac
                            proprietatem</rs>, res et predia que a nostris precessoribus collata
                        sunt et confirmata ac corroborata, confirmare et corroborare studuimus et de
                        nostris iuris proprietate in monachorum sumptum cortes et cellas contulimus,
                        quatinus sedulo orationes pro nobis <rs key="#marriage">coniugeque</rs>
                        nostra <persName key="#marriage" ref="#people/1301">Adelheida</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filioque</rs> nostro <rs key="#Emperor/king">rege</rs>
                        <persName key="#Emperor/king #childOf" ref="#people/239">Ottone</persName>
                        ibidem ad dominum dirigantur. Igitur cortes et cellas <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">masaricia</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sortes</rs>
                        <rs key="#Royal_slave">familiamque utriusque sexus</rs> que actenus
                        tenuerunt omniaque precepta ab antecessoribus nostris conlata omniaque
                        instrumenta confirmamus pleniterque corroboramus et, quoniam prefatum
                        coenobium in nostram devenit potestatem et proprietatem, et que a pravis
                        ablata sunt hominibus et alia quibus indigentiam explere valeant, in usum
                        fratrum per hoc nostrum preceptum concedimus donamus adque largimus,
                        videlicet cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1512"><placeName ref="#places/1949"
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                >Benedicti</placeName></orgName>, cortem de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/334"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/764">Palea</placeName></geogName>, cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/303">sancti Stephani in <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#places/757">Monticlo</placeName></orgName> et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/302">sanctae Marie in <placeName
                                ref="#places/756"
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                >Lamulas</placeName></orgName> cum suis pertinentiis, cortem de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/331"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/760">Mustia</placeName></geogName> et corticellam de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/335"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1951">Titinano</placeName></geogName> et in <placeName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #Angaria" ref="#places/1952">Cerri</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Coloni/tenants #Angaria">angariales</rs> et curticellam in
                            <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/761"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/2315">Fereniano</geogName></placeName> nec non et
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1516">cellam Salvatoris</orgName> in <placeName
                            ref="#places/2734">Uibugnano</placeName> et corticellam de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/332"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Cuniclo</placeName></geogName> cum ipso <rs key="#Houses"
                            >caiolo</rs> de Portiano et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1455">sancti Stephani</orgName> in <placeName
                            ref="#places/430">Terquino</placeName> seu etiam <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2334">cellam <orgName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    ><placeName
                                    key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >sancti Seueri</placeName></orgName> super <rs key="#Lakes"
                                >lacum</rs>
                        </geogName>cum ipsa corticella de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/333"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Bisentio</placeName></geogName>, cellam etiam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sancti Miniati</orgName> nec et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sancti Petri in <placeName>Garmarita</placeName></orgName> et cell[am]
                        sancte <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >Mariae de Ualeriano</orgName> cum ipsis rebus de Corticione cum omnibus
                        adiacentiis et pertinentiis earum atque cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2309"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >sancte Marie ad Offena</placeName></geogName> et corticellam
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2310"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >sancti Simeonis</placeName></geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2311"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >sanctum Petrum in Ceruaria</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus rebus
                        et familiis ad eas in integrum pertinentibus vel respicientibus; denique
                        etiam concedimus ad predictum coenobium omnia <rs key="#Decima">decima</rs>
                        frea et <rs>iudiciaria</rs> et omnem conpositionem et <rs
                            key="#Public_exactions">exibitionem</rs> publicam ex omnibus manentibus
                        predicti monasterii ob remedium animarum nostrarum in usum peregrinorum ad
                        portam monasterii clamantium. Precepimus etiam et statuimus ut deinceps in
                        futurum haec nostra confirmatio atque donatio a posteris nostris inconvulsa
                        maneat et inlibata, et ut nullus dux marchio c[om]es aut ulla regni nostri
                        magna parvaque persona in domos vel res predicti coenobii violentiam inferat
                        aut famulos flagellare vel angariare presumat neque de predictis rebus ullam
                        minorationem facere satagat, sed liceat abbatem sanctamque congregationem
                        predictas cortes et cellas cum earum integritatibus tenere omnium
                        inquietudine remota. Si quis hoc nostrum preceptum violare temptaverit, se
                        conpositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras centum</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem kamere nostre</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem sancte
                            congregacioni predicti coenobii</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur et
                        diligentius observetur, manibus propriis corroborantes anuli nostri
                        inpressione subter iussimus insigniri. Signum domni Ottonis invictissimi
                        imperatoris (M.) <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Liutulfus"
                                >Liutulfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> advicem <persName
                            key="#Archchaplain"><name ref="Bruno">Brunonis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archchaplain">archicappellani</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. (SR.)
                        (SI. D.) Data VIIII. kal. mar. anno dominicae incarnationis DCCCCLXII,
                        indictione V, anno regni serenissimi regis Ottonis XXVII, imperii primo;
                        actum <placeName>Rigiano</placeName>; in Christi nomine feliciter amen.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
